  <description><![CDATA[<p>Commanding superb views over Lugano and the lake, the Continental Park is an historic hotel with lots of atmosphere and excellent facilities for its star category. In a convenient location, the town centre and lakeside are reached within a few minutes by nearby funicular or short downhill walk, and the railway station is a minute’s walk away. The hotel’s wonderful lush gardens and large outdoor swimming pool provide a great spot for relaxing in this sunny region. Our prices are based on bed and breakfast.</p>]]></description>
